Front-End Engineer / UI Developer We are looking for a skilled UI developer to join our front-end development team. The ideal candidate should be passionate about technology and solving problems in an innovative way as well as being results-focused. In this role, you will be responsible for developing and implementing user interface components using Angular or React concepts.
